***** Code pertaining to axion minicluster simulations *****

-- Gadget-MatRad: modified version of Gadget which calculates the 
                  Hubble based on matter and radiation density 

-- ICs: write scripts for field -> txt and txt -> snapshot

-- GadgetAnimations: scipts to read snapshot files and plot density
                     fields or scatter plots using povray

-- Halo-Analysis: halo mass function and halo density profile calculators
